  "content_html": "<p class=\"mobile-date-eyebrow\">21st July 2026</p>\n<div class=\"beat beat-sighting\">\n\n\n<div class=\"beat-content\">\n  <div class=\"beat-row1\">\n    <a class=\"beat-label sighting\" href=\"/elsewhere/sighting/\">Sighting</a>\n    <span class=\"beat-title\">12:51 PM</span>\n    <span class=\"beat-commit\">&mdash; California Sea Lion, in San Francisco County, US, CA</span>\n  </div>\n  <captioned-image-gallery class=\"sighting-detail-gallery\" max-row-items=\"2\">\n    <figure><a href=\"https://static.inaturalist.org/photos/702321069/large.jpg\"><img src=\"https://static.inaturalist.org/photos/702321069/large.jpg\" alt=\"California Sea Lion\" loading=\"lazy\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1365\"></a><figcaption><a href=\"https://www.inaturalist.org/observations/383713864\" title=\"View observation on iNaturalist\">California Sea Lion</a></figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"https://static.inaturalist.org/photos/702321114/large.jpg\"><img src=\"https://static.inaturalist.org/photos/702321114/large.jpg\" alt=\"California Sea Lion\" loading=\"lazy\" data-width=\"2048\" data-height=\"1365\"></a><figcaption><a href=\"https://www.inaturalist.org/observations/383713864\" title=\"View observation on iNaturalist\">California Sea Lion</a></figcaption></figure>\n  </captioned-image-gallery>\n<div class=\"beat-note blogmark-body\"><p>We took some visiting family to Pier 39 to see the sea lions. They're somehow always even fun than I remember them being last time.</p></div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"entryFooter\">Posted <a href=\"/2026/Jul/21/\">21st July 2026</a> at 7:51 pm</div>\n<p class=\"edit-page-link\" data-admin-url=\"/admin/blog/beat/4786/\"></p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n</div> <!-- #primary -->\n\n<div id=\"secondary\">\n\n\n\n</div> <!-- #secondary -->\n</div> <!-- #wrapper -->\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div id=\"ft\">\n    <ul>\n      <li><a href=\"/about/#disclosures\">Disclosures</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/about/#about-site\">Colophon</